      <h2>Classical Weapons of the <span class="chinese-char">俠</span></h2>

      <div class="icon-feature-row">
        <div class="icon-feature"><span class="icon-feature-icon">🗡️</span><div class="icon-feature-text"><strong><span class="chinese-char">劍</span> Jiàn — Straight Sword</strong><br>The "gentleman's weapon" (<span class="chinese-char">君子之器</span>). Associated with cultivation, grace, and nobility. The finest swords are named and carry their own legends.</div></div>
